						               													<description>&amp;quot;Spiele Minis&amp;quot; is a series of small surprise boxes (i.e., you don't know what you get) from Ravensburger. They are meant to be carry-on or gifts, suitable for children (&amp;quot;Mitbringspiel&amp;quot;). Some of the cubes contain actual games, others contain magic tricks, puzzles etc.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Content: 8 big cards, 8 small cards, 1 pawn, 1 die.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The big cards are placed in a circle face up. Small cards are placed in the center face down. In a turn you roll the die and advance the pawn. Then you must try to reveal the small card that matches the picture in the big card where the pawn is. If you do so you can keep the small card. If the small card is already in front of another player you take it from him. If you are the one holding the small card requested, then you win!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
